PrecisOrder Amending THE FISHING ZONES OF CANADA (ZONES 4 AND 5) ORDER by a) updating the geographical coordinates defining the fishing zones prescribed in this Order, as a result of an adjustment to the dividing line between Canada and Greenland in the Davis Strait and Baffin Bay, b) replacing the two separate and outdated geodetic systems, c) improving the systems for navigation and position and d) ensuring the continuation of good relations with Denmark.
